cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
No title, runs terrible, name yer price.
313,000 miles on this baby. Diesel. German. Fick ja.
This thing's been run from Alaska to Florida in an speed-induced 39 hour beeline. If you want the drugs we found under the rear reclining seat, well, that costs extra.
Not for sale. The owner of the lot just wants you to know what he drives.
